","msg":"<blockquote>仲咩年代呀？一定要竹門對竹門，木門對木門？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中意咪拍拖一齊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定要搵得多錢先可以同人一齊架咩？<br />\n會唔會太過商業化呀？<br />\n<br />\n只要個女仔有努力返工，唔係做廢人等人養，我覺得都可以接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  當然心地一定要好，禮節要做足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果大家都可以堅持，真係要去到結婚嘅地步，佢老母最後都要讓步架啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多人都咁諗<br />\n我條女比較窮 住公屋<br />\n我自己屋企就中等 有樓收下租<br />\n當時同條女拍拖我老母都叫我快d分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見親面都講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後來 我其他親戚話我條女幾好，去到佢地到會幫佢地汁屋(我放假去親戚到住 帶埋條女)<br />\n我老母態度180度改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲叫我出街唔好要人洗錢 人地無錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f809b93caee79ff9215d58c43e3e60d18911c3","tid":480760,"uid":110319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T04:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>推爆條窮臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原本覺得佢唔係臭雞 只係思想幼稚<br />\n點知有巴打搵到佢 一腳踏緊幾船 仲問簡邊個好<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢度 真係全部都係雞<br />\n呢班港女 睇死佢地又會死撐 「女仔更係想嫁好d啦」<br />\n<br />\n掉番轉 男既一個踏幾船 就tag人賤男 花心<br />\n難道男既又唔想娶好d?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果呢個唔係故仔既話<br />\n真心希望佢男友醒覺，玩完呢d就好一腳伸開去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多女扮乖呃傻仔,<br />\n不過扮傻扮信 d 女、一玩厭就飛/踏船男仔都唔少,<br />\n格食格、都算天理遁環"},{"pid":"3f595c2bba2c510d1ef6b7d0afa26128c0b74cbd","tid":480760,"uid":7929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T04:14:12.000Z","msg":"你地係兩個世界既人"},{"pid":"40cc0fe50ddac2867fc3457cb980be84e2c8046f","tid":480760,"uid":110319,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T04:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得嗰廿歲女，人地話娶佢佢就信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地唔當面反枱俾說話佢聽只不過係覺得自己個仔遲早會同條女分手唔勞氣住咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n清心水清 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男人唔出聲、好多港女真係當人傻,<br />\n男人食厭+睇夠 d 女既馬騮戲自然會扔, d 女就話人地嘥左自己青春辜負左自己、講到好似只有佢有付出過咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 臨尾都要控訴人地一鑊、催眠自己啱晒、人地錯晒, 自我感覺良好"},{"pid":"e131b2343b8bd06cddcbcfef88b9612003a7ffb3","tid":480760,"uid":110319,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T04:41:10.000Z","msg":"大部份港女:<br />\n<br />\n如果男人條件好、去滾都忍到、只要有人養、有小三四都可以當睇唔到,<br />\n仲會將自己既貪婪包裝成 &quot;愛、包容、知情識趣、睇下我做人女友/老婆幾叻, 大家黎認同下我既愛有幾偉大啦&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果男人條件一般, 就誅多限制、嫌嫌尖尖挑挑剔剔,<br />\n讚自己既說話亦會改成 &quot;佢咁多缺點、我都忍緊佢、我付出左幾多架, 大家都照樣黎認同下我既愛好偉大啦&quot;..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大部份港女都話自己最真、講到只有自己先識得咩叫 '愛' 咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,<br />\n成日話男人物化女人, 往往明明係女人自己物化自己、又要賴落男人度"},{"pid":"22defca6085e328c7c409a432d48ac37c51c739a","tid":480760,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T05:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲咩年代呀？一定要竹門對竹門，木門對木門？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中意咪拍拖一齊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定要搵得多錢先可以同人一齊架咩？<br />\n會唔會太過商業化呀？<br />\n<br />\n只要個女仔有努力返工，唔係做廢人等人養，我覺得都可以接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  當然心地一定要好，禮節要做足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果大家都可以堅持，真係要去到結婚嘅地步，佢老母最後都要讓步架啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫佢口做乜姐，佢一腳踏兩船騎牛揾馬臭雞黎，根本無愛可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5405f04f7bffad7c9c7881957ce9bcf98cf875af","tid":480760,"uid":10719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:07:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">不過如果我聰明啲成為到佢同學<br />\n或者佢平凡啲同我一齊入政府做同一份工<br />\n可能所有野都會smooth啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來就係因為咁所以想條仔降grade陪佢過人世<br />\n都幾自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"827cc651d88362b91a955d04e08b44069f3524b2","tid":480760,"uid":10719,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:11:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲咩年代呀？一定要竹門對竹門，木門對木門？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中意咪拍拖一齊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定要搵得多錢先可以同人一齊架咩？<br />\n會唔會太過商業化呀？<br />\n<br />\n只要個女仔有努力返工，唔係做廢人等人養，我覺得都可以接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  當然心地一定要好，禮節要做足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果大家都可以堅持，真係要去到結婚嘅地步，佢老母最後都要讓步架啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多人都咁諗<br />\n我條女比較窮 住公屋<br />\n我自己屋企就中等 有樓收下租<br />\n當時同條女拍拖我老母都叫我快d分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見親面都講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後來 我其他親戚話我條女幾好，去到佢地到會幫佢地汁屋(我放假去親戚到住 帶埋條女)<br />\n我老母態度180度改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲叫我出街唔好要人洗錢 人地無錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n[member] 依啲係真正嘅入得廚房 出得廳堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係唔係賢妻良母人地有眼睇, 係人地講, 唔係自己讚自己嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔似樓主不停讚自己踩低人地父母白鴿眼, <br />\n鬧完一大輪之後話自己無怪對方父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n扮大方得「睇」<br />\n<br />\n仲話自己成日睇書, 成日睇書都可以咁無文化,<br />\n真心想知佢睇咩書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慌唔係尋夢園個啲濕鳩愛情小說咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有錢仔 + 窮家女 然後有錢仔應該不顧一切同全世界為敵都堅持要娶佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e484cd50cbf45ffbe5b9bb71cc142895b7f271e4","tid":480760,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:16:40.000Z","msg":"痴撚線人地老豆搵100k <br />\n想個仔揀個好少少嘅有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n父權係咁架啦，你條氣唔順咪做好D囉<br />\n不嬲拍拖到結婚都唔係兩個人嘅事<br />\n你估你男朋友冇壓力嘅咩<br />\n日日同你去完街返屋企都比人哦"},{"pid":"4ed09b78f472561e892c9abb2d74ccc8e3979d30","tid":480760,"uid":2355,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:27:15.000Z","msg":"我屋企住公屋<br />\n我同我細佬都係大學畢業<br />\n細佬條女HD畢業 我都唔中意啦（雖然唔關我事）<br />\n更何況人地書香世家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依個年代大學係基本盤黎 你話我白鴿眼都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e9bd8f2a86a3997419690c7160c5053aad474f","tid":480760,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:35:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屋企住公屋<br />\n我同我細佬都係大學畢業<br />\n細佬條女HD畢業 我都唔中意啦（雖然唔關我事）<br />\n更何況人地書香世家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依個年代大學係基本盤黎 你話我白鴿眼都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同你差唔多<br />\n都係公屋仔 讀緊一大<br />\n之前個ex 入唔到大學<br />\n我老母暗示姖唔滿意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 老母對我影響力係零 分手同呢樣無關"}]}